{
  "stem": "1400.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We got hold of a bucket of water occasionally, and we washed ourselves, several of us, with a piece of rag.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And that was our-- extent of our cleaning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all had lice, and we contracted-- I contracted typhus, so I was separated, quarantined, and I had to go in one of these A-frame barracks, who everybody who had fever-- high fever and typhus-- typhoid?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Typhus?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Typhus.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that week or 10 days I was in there, I don't know how long, high fever, very little food or water.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever they brought in, the other fellows, and distributed among us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "About a week or 10 days later, when I came to, I was-- ample room around me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- when I was taken in there, it-- we were shoulder to shoulder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were ample room around me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rest of them were carried out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As I say, as I walked out, I took off my trousers, and both of my shin was covered with lice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was like an ant hill on my shin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I when I swept it off, my skin went with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yet one nice thing happened in, in-- with us in Kaufering that-- I don't know if the American or the International Red Cross was let in for inspection.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As I said, this was the very end of World War II.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The, the heavy artillery was-- we were hearing it all day, all night by then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Red Cross was let in, and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they distributed some blankets and some food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Still remember getting a can of Borden's milk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I cherished it for days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It, it really helped me survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
